%e A000579 For A = {1,2,3,4,5,6} subsets with 5 elements are {1,2,3,4,5}, {1,2,3,4,6}, {1,2,3,5,6}, {1,2,4,5,6}, {1,3,4,5,6}, {2,3,4,5,6}. Sum of 2 smallest elements of each subset: a(6) = (1+2) + (1+2) + (1+2) + (1+2) + (1+3) + (2+3) = 21 = 3*C(6+1,6) = 3*A000579(6+1). - _Serhat Bulut_, Oktay Erkan Temizkan, Mar 13 2015
